  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hi @vvo, sorry for the response time too.\nIndeed, for my product index , I have a facet 'categories.fr.0 ' and use a hierarchical widget instantsearch for the categories . So I wanted to have a page listing products with a category selected during initialization.\nFinaly, the algolia support gave me the solution:\n\n``` javascript\nvar search = instantsearch({\n  [...],\n  searchParameters: {\n    hierarchicalFacetsRefinements: {\n      'categories.fr.0': ['Revêtement > Éléments de décor > Poignées de portes']\n    }\n  }\n});\n```\n",
    "created_at": "2016-02-17T16:50:52Z",
